    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p> <p>Boil a kettle</p> <p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p> <p>&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pesto-mac-n-cheese-with-tenderstem-and-spinach/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium-low heat&nbsp;</p> <p>Once melted, add the<strong>&nbsp;sliced onion&nbsp;</strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6-8 min or until softened&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pesto-mac-n-cheese-with-tenderstem-and-spinach/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>macaroni</strong> to&nbsp;a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p> <p>Cook the <strong>macaroni</strong> for 5 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p> <p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic&nbsp;</strong></p> <p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p> <p>&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pesto-mac-n-cheese-with-tenderstem-and-spinach/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>macaroni</strong> has had 5 min, add the <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> and cook for 2 min further until everything's tender</p> <p>Once done, drain the <strong>macaroni</strong> and <strong>broccoli</strong>, reserving 300ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml]</span> of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pesto-mac-n-cheese-with-tenderstem-and-spinach/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>onion</strong>&nbsp;has softened, add the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p> <p>Add the <strong>drained pasta</strong> and <strong>broccoli</strong> to the pan with the <strong>cr&egrave;me fra&icirc;che</strong>&nbsp;and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper&nbsp;</strong></p> <p>Add the <strong>basil nut</strong>&nbsp;<strong>pesto pots</strong>, <strong>grated cheddar</strong> and 200ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml]</span> of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong> and give everything a good old mix up&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pesto-mac-n-cheese-with-tenderstem-and-spinach/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>baby leaf&nbsp;</strong><strong>spinach</strong> and cook for 1 min further, stirring until <span class=\"text-highlight\">it's</span> wilted</p> <p>Tip: add a splash more pasta water if the sauce is looking a bit dry &ndash; remember it will thicken in the oven!&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pesto-mac-n-cheese-with-tenderstem-and-spinach/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Transfer the <strong>mac 'n' cheese</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish&nbsp;</strong></p> <p>Top with the <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong></p> <p>Put the dish in the oven for 10 min or until bubbling and crispy</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/pesto-mac-n-cheese-with-tenderstem-and-spinach/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Remove the<strong> pesto mac 'n' cheese</strong> from the oven and leave to stand until cooled slightly</p> <p>Serve the <strong>pesto mac 'n' cheese&nbsp;</strong></p> <p>Top with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper</strong>&nbsp;</p> <p>Enjoy!</p> <p>&nbsp;</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
